  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nAnvil\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nAs of https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/pull/3198/commits/6e5a613e21f969bfd82afdd7f55b7cba96c1b2be, Anvil's `debug_traceTransaction` differs from geth in several places which are also on screenshots:\r\n1. <s>Incorrect memory state during `MSTORE`</s> It was fixed for Geth in https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/commit/97f308a98f9f2f557a0815665f6497eac8f469fd but my RPC uses Erigon which doesn't have these changes and still does memory expansion **before** tracing: https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/blob/cd8cad6a8908970fa092aa5e2dcd8f38aedccd89/core/vm/interpreter.go#L316-L323\r\n2. Remaining gas and instruction gas cost calculated incorrectly: https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/6e5a613e21f969bfd82afdd7f55b7cba96c1b2be/evm/src/executor/inspector/tracer.rs#L138-L139\r\n<img width=\"1143\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5773434/190135701-370e66c6-67cf-4ac4-9df2-6cd572c7c9df.png\">\r\n<img width=\"1161\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5773434/190135181-a1144e75-cb24-4007-994a-f52178da07ae.png\">\r\n",
